    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo includes a exclusive area with some jumping and grappling puzzle platforming areas and some fun physics based objects to use to your advantage to reach the end. The area included is not in the main game. The main game has cutscenes, multiple areas, lots of collectables and even a boss! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/91f1a9e79898896510c31409cb69cfac.poster.avif?t=1727755244\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/91f1a9e79898896510c31409cb69cfac.webm?t=1727755244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/91f1a9e79898896510c31409cb69cfac.mp4?t=1727755244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use fun and experimental controls to roll ball frog around awesome environments!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Ball Frogs tongue as a grappling hook to grab, swing and fling Ball Frog through the map!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check Points are used so you don't loose progress and will save your checkpoint for the next time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since this game uses physics a lot, we have many mechanics that can bounce, swing and even pop you as you play through the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/4becbbb541f3017f60ef874a60cf48b6.poster.avif?t=1727755244\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/4becbbb541f3017f60ef874a60cf48b6.webm?t=1727755244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845580/extras/4becbbb541f3017f60ef874a60cf48b6.mp4?t=1727755244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The in game currency &quot;Flies&quot;  can be collected throughout the game and can be spent in the shop to buy cosmetic hats and skins!</p>",
